               <provenance>According to Additio 1, the donor of the book
                     is ʾabbā Ḫāyla Mikāʾel and the commissioner
                     is Getayä Šäte. The name of ʾabbā Ḫāyla
                     Mikāʾel has been also added into the supplication formula on 3ra, interlineally on 19vb, 26va, 35va, 40va and into the concluding supplication formula
                     on 52ra, in the main hand, in strong
                     vermilion.</provenance></history>
